## Development Setup

1. Fork and clone the repository:

   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/{{ github_username }}/{{ repository_name }}.git
   cd {{ repository_name }}
   ```

2. Install dependencies using uv:

   ```bash
   uv sync --group dev
   ```
